OL,3,CGovernment plans more benefit cuts as
OL,4,COBR downgrades welfare savings
OL,6,FIt was awkward for Work and Pensions
OL,7,FSecretary Liz Kendall to have to
OL,8,Fannounce major changes to welfare
OL,9,Fwithout putting a number on it.
OL,11,FI found myself challenging her on how
OL,12,Fmany people would be hit, and how the
OL,13,Freforms added up to the #5 billion net
OL,14,Fsavings she had floated.
OL,16,FKendall could not respond.
OL,18,FHer answer instead was ` we have to
OL,19,Fwait for the Office For Budget
OL,20,FResponsibility (OBR).
