OL,6,FAnd now the quango has come up with
OL,7,Fthe goods but they fall well short of
OL,8,Fthe government's hopes.
OL,10,FI can reveal that the OBR has judged
OL,11,Fthe net savings from the welfare
OL,12,Fpackage to be at #3.4 billion,
OL,13,Fsignificantly below the amount that
OL,14,Fgovernment analysts had laid out.
