OL,3,CGovernment plans more benefit cuts as
OL,4,COBR downgrades welfare savings
OL,6,FSources tell me that the calculation
OL,7,Fincludes an extra #500 million saving
OL,8,Fby Rachel Reeves. The new package will
OL,9,Fsee incapacity benefits (the higher
OL,10,Frate of universal credit) for new
OL,11,Fclaimants frozen until 2030, after an
OL,12,Finitial cut, and will also slightly
OL,13,Freduce the basic rate of universal
OL,14,Fcredit in 2029 after an earlier
OL,15,Fincrease.
OL,17,FThe government must have assumed its
OL,18,Finitial package would save #6.4
OL,19,Fbillion growth with #1.4 billion
OL,20,Fploughed back in, giving them a net
OL,21,Fsaving of #5 billion.
