OL,6,FInstead, the OBR calculated a growth
OL,7,Fsaving of #4.3 billion from the
OL,8,Foriginal package. By adding on another
OL,9,F#500m in savings, and spending #1.4
OL,10,Fbillion, the OBR arrived at the lower
OL,11,Fnet figure.
